VPC1 -> ip 192.168.10.10 255.255.255.0 192.168.10.1
VPC2 -> ip 192.168.20.10 255.255.255.0 192.168.20.1
VPC3 -> ip 192.168.30.10 255.255.255.0 192.168.30.1
